{"id":"person.zimmerman.john_paul","node_type":"person","display_name":"John Paul Zimmerman","index_names":["Zimmerman, John Paul"],"name_variants":[],"branches":["zimmerman"],"role":"ancestor","confidence":"strong","privacy":"public_deceased","public_anchor":"person.zimmerman.john_paul","display":{"details":"John born 9 Mar 1842 in Bavaria/Germany; Catherine born 30 Jan 1839 in Bavaria/Germany. FamilySearch indexes their marriage in 1864 in Bavaria and John's death on 12 Jun 1926 at Beloit Township, Mitchell County, Kansas.{{cite:src.john-paul-zimmerman-familysearch.68be8f2c}} Their 1880 household was in Norfolk, Madison County, Nebraska.{{cite:src.1880-madison-county-nebraska-census-index.9d41b03f}}","identity":"Doyle's Zimmerman great-grandparents.","title_override":"John Paul Zimmerman + Catherine M. Zinkle/Zinkl","vitals":"John · b. 9 Mar 1842, Bavaria/Germany – Catherine · b. 30 Jan 1839, Bavaria/Germany – m. 1864, Bavaria – John · d. 12 Jun 1926, Beloit Township, Mitchell County, Kansas – res. 1880, Norfolk, Madison County, Nebraska"}}
{"id":"person.zimmerman.leonard","node_type":"person","display_name":"Leonard Henry Zimmerman","index_names":["Zimmerman, Leonard Henry"],"name_variants":[],"branches":["zimmerman"],"role":"ancestor","confidence":"documented","privacy":"public_deceased","public_anchor":"person.zimmerman.leonard","display":{"details":"1903-1968, Doyle's father by cemetery profile.{{cite:src.doyle-jule-zimmerman-find-a-grave.a6b1ff2c}} Elizabeth Catherine Nauer Zimmerman's cemetery profile lists Leonard Henry among the children of Michael John Zimmerman and Elizabeth, closing the main American link in the surname chain pending a primary certificate/census pull.{{cite:src.elizabeth-catherine-nauer-zimmerman-find-a-grave.48bab423}}","identity":"Doyle's father; American Zimmerman link to Michael and Elizabeth.","vitals":"b. 1903 – d. 1968"}}
{"id":"person.zimmerman.michael","node_type":"person","display_name":"Michael John Zimmerman Sr.","index_names":["Zimmerman, Michael John Sr."],"name_variants":[],"branches":["zimmerman"],"role":"ancestor","confidence":"strong","privacy":"public_deceased","public_anchor":"person.zimmerman.michael","display":{"ahnen_override":"Z-4·5","cameos":[{"alt":"Shared Zimmerman headstone for Michael J. and Elizabeth A. at Selden Cemetery","credit_label":"Shared stone: Find a Grave","credit_url":"https://www.findagrave.com/memorial/69631173/elizabeth_catherine-zimmerman","height":353,"src":"images/people/elizabeth-nauer-zimmerman.jpg","width":480}],"details":"Michael born 25 Oct 1869, indexed at Wuerttemberger Hof, Mainhardt. FamilySearch says he married Elizabeth Catherine Nauer at Cawker City, Kansas, 19 Nov 1895; Elizabeth's own Nauer card carries the Selden Cemetery stone and birth-year conflict.{{cite:src.michael-john-zimmerman-sr-familysearch.8c643069}}{{cite:src.selden-cemetery-ksgenweb.82a81b07}}","identity":"Doyle's paternal grandparents; Elizabeth's own Nauer row is {{link:#person.nauer.elizabeth|Z-5}}.","title_override":"Michael John Zimmerman Sr. + Elizabeth Catherine Nauer","vitals":"Michael · b. 25 Oct 1869, Wuerttemberger Hof, Mainhardt – m. 19 Nov 1895, Cawker City, Kansas"}}
